 blue Team Finucane T-shirts, it felt like home from home.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Williams\", \"score\": 0.8605105044278003, \"rank\": 0.16210086321385317, \"text\": \"Rory\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Yung\", \"score\": 0.9976578497630295, \"rank\": 0.002347648783007295, \"text\": \"Susie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Yung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Yung\"}, {\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.431554744393256e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crowd\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"its support\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"her parents\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"a hired campervan\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"navy blue Team Finucane T-shirts\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she went into the event brimming with confidence from one gold already in the team sprint.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the team sprint\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Come the final of the keirin, an athlete l